Mödling.title: Mödling
Mödling.byline: Mödling is a city of 20,500 people (2018) in Lower Austria, on the southern outskirts of Vienna.

Mödlareuth.title: Mödlareuth
Mödlareuth.byline: Mödlareuth is a small, unincorporated German village divided between the towns of Töpen, Upper Franconia, Bavaria and Gefell, Thuringia.
